### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Register School
POST {{baseUrl}}/schools/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Delhi Public School",
  "password": "password123",
  "confirmPassword": "password123",
  "address": "123 School Street, Central Delhi",
  "city": "New Delhi",
  "state": "Delhi",
  "pincode": "110001",
  "principalName": "Dr. Rajesh Kumar",
  "contactEmail": "principal@dpsdelhi.edu.in",
  "contactPhone": "9876543210"
}

### Login School
POST {{baseUrl}}/schools/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Delhi Public School",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get All Schools
GET {{baseUrl}}/schools?page=1&limit=10

### Register Student (Replace schoolId with actual ID from school registration)
POST {{baseUrl}}/students/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

